    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Way Of Animals: This World Will Show You the Way that Animals Surviv</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras/24aea4477ca4fadea504bc17ec0c753c.avif?t=1733550140\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras_big/24aea4477ca4fadea504bc17ec0c753c.avif?t=1733550140 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Way Of Animals was created and designed for players who are looking for a place to feel like the leader, the protector, the one who guides the herd, a place where you can be the best in the entire African savannah.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Great Multiplayer System</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras/00a8e8d669c5f3fb21890174e19f0f9d.avif?t=1733550140\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras_big/00a8e8d669c5f3fb21890174e19f0f9d.avif?t=1733550140 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vast environmental protection reserve called Crater. A place where several different species can coexist in total freedom. Be careful, not all the animals that live here are peaceful, some are just waiting for the most opportune moment to make their attack.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Life Cycle System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras/3447a7f7ffbdecd13aade77276944227.avif?t=1733550140\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras_big/3447a7f7ffbdecd13aade77276944227.avif?t=1733550140 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live and survive from the smallest of the Crater's inhabitants and progress with our Life Cycle System until you become the strongest and most dominant species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Danger is Everywhere</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras/4b97d15dcd882924a97ef0f00cd37c62.avif?t=1733550140\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras_big/4b97d15dcd882924a97ef0f00cd37c62.avif?t=1733550140 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be prepared for surprise attacks, danger lurks behind every rock. Your cubs will need all your skills to protect them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Great PVP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras/dd1ee9776eeb1ec20d52fe4a7043dc50.avif?t=1733550140\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193510/extras_big/dd1ee9776eeb1ec20d52fe4a7043dc50.avif?t=1733550140 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces with friends to take down on bigger prey.</p>",
